metadata.name: The First Link
metadata.description: https://ipfs.io/QmXTuoeQiRiiXvcHhmXn42MJo33LAXKehWmm9fHknvRj2G/Animetas_-_First_Link.pdf -- The first book written to be published on-chain, "The First Link" is part 1 of 3 of a planned Trilogy following the Blockchain zombies and their origins in the Animeta's universe! Please enjoy this Scifi-thriller set in a dystopian world where corporations begin to form their own nations with absolute authority and about the survival of those trapped within! Written by No Sleep (@belsgarde on twitter) and Silent (@M4flyer on twitter), for the Animeta's community, we hope you enjoy our book!
